data.description: Exquisitely maintained 4-bedroom residence in immaculate condition! This delightful property boasts 2 1/2 baths and abundant storage throughout. The spacious family room features a Cathedral ceiling and a charming wood burning fireplace, complemented by lustrous wood floors that gracefully extend down the hallway. A well-appointed breakfast bar with cabinets seamlessly connects to the dining area and the expansive kitchen, which showcases a large island, elegant granite countertops, and new Kitchen-Aid appliances, including double ovens, cooktop, dishwasher, sink, and faucets. The kitchen offers an a great amount of counter space and storage, including a walk-in pantry and a utility storage closet. The laundry room is conveniently equipped with an exterior door, providing easy access from outside. It also includes a sink, cabinets, and space for an extra refrigerator/freezer. A generously sized formal dining area, perfectly adaptable as an office, adds to the versatility of this home. All bedrooms are spacious and feature ample closet space. The bathrooms are tastefully appointed with granite countertops and updated fixtures. The 2-car oversized garage is a haven for storage enthusiasts, featuring ample cabinets, a workbench, and additional storage space. Stepping outside, you'll discover a large covered patio leading to a charming shop. The shop includes electricity, built-in cabinets, storage, and attic space and RV hook-up. For added privacy, the property is fully fenced, thoughtfully designed on each side. This home is a true gem, combining comfort, elegance, and a peaceful setting for your enjoyment. Private lake access.
